---
title: Crêpes Françaises Serves 2 | with Warm Plum Compote and Honey Whipped Cream
description: The slightly more sophisticated (but just as delicious) version of pancakes, crêpes are perfect for when you feel like stepping up your weekend brunch game. They're smothered in a warm cinnamon plum compote and lightly-sweetened honey whipped cream for a truly delectable bite!
